q4","type":"text","x":50,"y":284,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"          ≈  2.116  +  0.324  +  2.883  + ...  ≈  6.8","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"denom_note","type":"text","x":50,"y":302,"strokeColor":"#c07000","text":"γ is symmetric (γᵢⱼ = γⱼᵢ), so ALL channels influence channel i's normalization","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"step3_label","type":"text","x":30,"y":340,"strokeColor":"#9c36b5","text":"STEP 2: add bias β₁ and take sqrt  →  final denominator","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"denom2_box","type":"rectangle","x":30,"y":362,"width":440,"height":55,"backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","strokeColor":"#9c36b5","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"denom2_eq","type":"text","x":50,"y":375,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"denom₁ = √(β₁ + Σⱼ γ₁ⱼ·wⱼ²)  =  √(1.0 + 6.8)  =  √7.8  ≈  2.79","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"denom2_note","type":"text","x":50,"y":398,"strokeColor":"#6a1f9a","text":"β₁ > 0 ensures we never divide by zero  (β is learned, constrained ≥ 2⁻⁵)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"step4_label","type":"text","x":30,"y":440,"strokeColor":"#0c8599","text":"STEP 3: divide  →  normalized output","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"out_box","type":"rectangle","x":30,"y":462,"width":440,"height":55,"backgroundColor":"#99e9f2","strokeColor":"#0c8599","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"out_eq","type":"text","x":50,"y":475,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"u₁ = w₁ / denom₁  =  2.3 / 2.79  ≈  0.82","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"out_note","type":"text","x":50,"y":499,"strokeColor":"#0c5e6e","text":"output magnitude is bounded — high-energy neighborhoods get more suppressed","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.851Z","version":1},{"id":"step5_label","type":"text","x":30,"y":540,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"STEP 4: repeat for every channel  →  GDN output vector","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"outvec_ch1","type":"rectangle","x":30,"y":562,"width":100,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#a5d8ff","strokeColor":"#1971c2","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"outvec_ch1_v","type":"text","x":60,"y":582,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"u₁ = 0.82","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"outvec_ch2","type":"rectangle","x":145,"y":562,"width":100,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","strokeColor":"#2f9e44","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"outvec_ch2_v","type":"text","x":165,"y":582,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"u₂ = -0.44","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"outvec_ch3","type":"rectangle","x":260,"y":562,"width":100,"height":50,"backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","strokeColor":"#e03131","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"outvec_ch3_v","type":"text","x":278,"y":582,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"u₃ = 0.61","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"dots_out","type":"text","x":378,"y":580,"strokeColor":"#888","text":"... (128 channels)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"key_insight","type":"text","x":30,"y":632,"strokeColor":"#e03131","text":"KEY INSIGHT: each channel's output depends on ALL channels' inputs at (m,n).\nThis captures cross-channel dependencies — impossible with pointwise ReLU.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.852Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_relu_box","type":"rectangle","x":530,"y":90,"width":260,"height":250,"backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","strokeColor":"#f08c00","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_relu_title","type":"text","x":570,"y":100,"strokeColor":"#f08c00","text":"vs. ReLU (pointwise)","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_relu_eq","type":"text","x":545,"y":130,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","text":"u₁ = max(0, w₁) = 2.3\nu₂ = max(0, w₂) = 0.0\nu₃ = max(0, w₃) = 3.1","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_relu_note1","type":"text","x":545,"y":210,"strokeColor":"#e03131","text":"✗ ignores channel 2 entirely\n   (negative → dead)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_relu_note2","type":"text","x":545,"y":258,"strokeColor":"#e03131","text":"✗ u₃=3.1 stays large even if\n   ALL other channels are huge\n   (no gain control!)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_relu_note3","type":"text","x":545,"y":310,"strokeColor":"#e03131","text":"✗ output statistics remain\n   heavy-tailed → bad for\n   entropy coding","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_gdn_box","type":"rectangle","x":530,"y":360,"width":260,"height":200,"backgroundColor":"#d3f9d8","strokeColor":"#2f9e44","strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":0,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_gdn_title","type":"text","x":590,"y":370,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"GDN (joint)","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_gdn_note1","type":"text","x":545,"y":398,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"✓ all channels suppress each other\n   (local gain control)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_gdn_note2","type":"text","x":545,"y":440,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"✓ output approx Gaussian even\n   when inputs are heavy-tailed","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_gdn_note3","type":"text","x":545,"y":478,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"✓ fewer stages needed for\n   same R-D performance","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"vs_gdn_note4","type":"text","x":545,"y":518,"strokeColor":"#2f9e44","text":"✓ spatially adaptive\n   (unlike batch norm)","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T12:49:48.853Z","version":1},{"id":"arr_ch1_denom","type":"arrow","x":122.60401331350783,"y":155.0856580228888,"width":0,"height":55,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","points":[[0,0],[54.4348305158415,44.82868395422241]],"start":{"id":"ch1_bo